<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>POST</title>
    <style>
      table {
        width: 600px;
      }
      th,
      td { 
        padding: 8px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      a {
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 4px 8px;
        color: white;
        background-color: maroon;
        border: none;
      }
      a:hover {
        color: maroon;
        background-color: white;
        border: 1px solid black;
      }
      a.information-user {
        border: none;
        background-color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: darkgreen;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Home Page</h1>

    <a href="/allpost">All-Post</a>
    <a href="/addnew"">Add New</a>
    <a href="/preview">Previews</a>
    <hr />
    <h3>Lecturers Page</h3>

    <p>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Omnis voluptate
      minima a unde assumenda laboriosam ex labore suscipit nihil. Eos
      asperiores adipisci officiis, aspernatur error vero saepe temporibus iusto
      quasi.
    </p>
    <div>
      <table border="1" cellspacing="0">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>id</th>
            <th>name</th>
            <th>subject</th>
            <th>age</th>
            <th>city</th>
      
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% Posts.forEach(post => { %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= post.id %></td>
            <td>
              <a
                class="information-user"
                href="/article/information/<%=post.id%>"
              >
                <%= post.name %>
              </a>
            </td>
            <td><%= post.subject %></td>
            <td><%= post.age %></td>
            <td><%= post.city %></td>
          </tr>
          <% }) %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
